room_title: Escape room "Vet Office" by Fuzzy Logic Escape Room in Chicago
review: I caught one of their games and had so much fun! There were some really clever puzzles, and my friends all had a blast! Can't wait to do it again!

room_title: Escape room "Vet Office" by Fuzzy Logic Escape Room in Chicago
review: Booked the Vet Office! Had a blast! Definitely challenges you and we were so lucky to have Andrew give us some hints along the way.

room_title: Escape room "Vet Office" by Fuzzy Logic Escape Room in Chicago
review: Fun for a group of teenagers. It's very challenging and they used all the given clues, but had a great time figuring it out together. I like that there were two separate rooms in the "Vet Room", so you could complete one room then move on to the other. The person there was very helpful and friendly. Would definitely go back there again.
